s from industry experts.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"main-content\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>What You'll Learn</h3>\n            <div class=\"course-info\">\n                <div class=\"course-item\">\n                    <h4>Full-Stack Development</h4>\n                    <p>Master both front-end and back-end technologies to build complete web applications.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"course-item\">\n                    <h4>Data Science & AI</h4>\n                    <p>Dive into data analysis, machine learning, and artificial intelligence with practical projects.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"course-item\">\n                    <h4>Mobile App Development</h4>\n                    <p>Create stunning iOS and Android applications using the latest frameworks.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"apply-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>\n            <a href=\"#\" class=\"cta-button\">Apply Now</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 CodeMaster Bootcamp. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}